summary: LETTER FROM TOM TUCKER, EXECUTIVE DIRECTOR `OF DAVIESS COUNTY CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, FORWARDED TO NHTSA BY SENATOR LUGAR OF INDIANA.   TUCKER EXPRESSED OPPOSITION   TO EARLY WARNING REPORT (EWR) REGULATION  THA T REQUIRED  MANUFACTURERS OF OVER 500 SMALL TO MEDIUM TRAILER COMPANIES  TO SUBMIT QUARTERLY  EARLY WARNING REPORTS TO NHTSA. SUCH REPORTING WOULD ECONOMICALLY HURT SOME OF THE TRAILER COMPANIES AND COULD PUT THEM OUT OF BUSINESS.  *AK
